msg: SOLR-2890: Fixed a bug that prevented omitNorms and omitTermFreqAndPositions options from being respected in some <fieldType/> declarations

author: rvesse
msg: Fix a bug in FusekiLib where safeParameter() would always check the 'dataset' parameter regardless of the parameter name passed.  This meant things like the RDF Data validator were broken because they'd receive a null instead of the parameter value and fall back to default behaviour e.g. trying to parse Turtle as NQuads
